title: How to use CSS masking
description: CSS masking gives you the option of using an image as a mask layer. This means that use can use an image, an SVG, or a gradient as your mask, to create interested effects without an image editor.

title: mask-image
description: The mask-image CSS property sets the image that is used as mask layer for an element.
